</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="nb">require</span> <span class="s1">&#39;date&#39;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">task</span> <span class="ss">:default</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="ss">:dev</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1"># Run Jekyll, access site at localhost:4000</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">desc</span> <span class="s1">&#39;Run Jekyll in development mode&#39;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">task</span> <span class="ss">:dev</span> <span class="k">do</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="nb">puts</span> <span class="s1">&#39;* Running Jekyll with auto-generation and server&#39;</span>
